name: Mrs Lady
text: I went to the courthouse today. I was assisted by Mrs Linda Floyd. I'm not sure if she was having a bad day or what but she was very rude, unprofessional, uncaring and unconcerned. Even my child could tell and questioned me about her disposition and behavior that she exhibited during my time there... I hope this gets addressed immediately!

name: Bill Frazier
text: I left a message at the probate office and my phone call was returned within minutes and Sylvia Davis provided 5 star service.  Great Job!!!

name: Laurie Nicholson
text: I am always amazed at how kind and helpful the clerks are, even though they have to deal in customer service all day, every day.

name: Kevin KD Doyle
text: I've been out on Parole since October 2006. Been through several different Parole Officer's. I've always been treated with respect n they try to help me when need be. ...... Definitely better than the alternative.

name: brandon brooks
text: Sucks. Long waits, hot waiting room. Supervisor has attitude that everyone there is irredeemable threash.
